{"tid":1062312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【炒車炒到仆街】【東張西望fake news】「公廁洗手液感染食肉菌」？原來根本係鳩吹","createTime":"2019-03-15T04:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T02:35:33.000Z","uid":138409,"like":136,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"be260f0c3f4d6e678fbf495a5ba50b5f2fb15c9f","tid":1062312,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:29:19.000Z","msg":"fact check<br />\n<a href=\"https://tfc-taiwan.org.tw/articles/404?fbclid=IwAR0utlVLGzOXihRxPpCgrUSMipljWVmiAiVL8G18twSBwiJeeY6SIa6DMhU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftfc-taiwan.org.tw%2Farticles%2F404%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0utlVLGzOXihRxPpCgrUSMipljWVmiAiVL8G18twSBwiJeeY6SIa6DMhU&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=77778a6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tfc-taiwan.org.tw/articles/404?fbclid=IwAR0utlVLGzOXihRxPpCgrUSMipljWVmiAiVL8G18twSBwiJeeY6SIa6DMhU</a><br />\n<br />\n今次真係要畀台灣記者credit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然平時連登成日笑人地啲風化案<br />\n但係今次班香港記者完全無fact check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係啊講緊你地啊<br />\n東張西望<br />\n<a href=\"http://programme.tvb.com/variety/scoop/episode/20190226/#page-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprogramme.tvb.com%2Fvariety%2Fscoop%2Fepisode%2F20190226%2F%23page-1&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=53a9ea43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://programme.tvb.com/variety/scoop/episode/20190226/#page-1</a><br />\n東方日報<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190223/bkn-20190223215730175-0223_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190223%2Fbkn-20190223215730175-0223_00822_001.html&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=dc6860be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190223/bkn-20190223215730175-0223_00822_001.html</a><br />\n晴報<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2277661/%E7%94%A8%E5%85%AC%E5%BB%81%E6%B4%97%E6%89%8B%E6%B6%B2%E6%9F%93%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%89%E8%8F%8C%2033%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E6%AF%80%E5%AE%B9%E9%95%B7%E8%A1%80%E7%98%A1%E9%9A%AA%E5%96%AA%E5%91%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2277661%2F%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25BB%2581%25E6%25B4%2597%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25B6%25B2%25E6%259F%2593%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%2582%2589%25E8%258F%258C%252033%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%25AF%2580%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%25A1%2580%25E7%2598%25A1%25E9%259A%25AA%25E5%2596%25AA%25E5%2591%25BD&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=034f2804\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2277661/%E7%94%A8%E5%85%AC%E5%BB%81%E6%B4%97%E6%89%8B%E6%B6%B2%E6%9F%93%E9%A3%9F%E8%82%89%E8%8F%8C%2033%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E6%AF%80%E5%AE%B9%E9%95%B7%E8%A1%80%E7%98%A1%E9%9A%AA%E5%96%AA%E5%91%BD</a><br />\n連登<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1035412/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1035412/page/1</a><br />\n仲有其他報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然公廁洗手液係咪污糟呢？好大機會係<br />\n但係當事人根本唔知自己係咪響公廁感染細菌，更加唔知感染咗乜嘢菌<br />\n成班就係度老吹，將外國小報啲料加油添醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6495184fd1b6d41a5350711b912fbd23e5b62c2","tid":1062312,"uid":138409,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f3vO06b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff3vO06b.jpg&h=b2c3a43d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">多家媒體引述外媒報導，美國女子Rachel Star Withers「用公廁洗手乳洗手 竟全身現血瘡、臉腐蝕如殭屍」。<br />\n查核中心向 Rachel Star Withers 本人求證，Rachel Star Withers 證實去年臉部肌膚受到感染，但「那些提到給皂器的部分完全是捏造的」。<br />\n因此，「她用公廁洗手乳洗手 竟全身現血瘡、臉腐蝕如殭屍」是「錯誤」訊息。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">背景</span><br />\n<br />\n多家媒體引述外媒報導：「她用公廁洗手乳洗手 竟全身現血瘡、臉腐蝕如殭屍」，內容描述美國一名女子瑞秋（Rachel Star Withers）「使用公廁所附的洗手乳洗手，沒想到竟感染了食肉細菌導致臉上出現血瘡，最後半張臉都遭啃食」&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n（台灣fake news cap圖從略）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">罪魁禍首</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6wqbYTc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6wqbYTc.jpg&h=42a139c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n查核<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">爭議點一：報導中之照片是否為真？是否真有 Rachel Star Withers 其人？</span><br />\n<br />\n查核中心根據報導內文及相關訊息，在社群網絡上找到 Rachel Star Withers 之 Youtube頻道<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/rachelstarlive\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fuser%2Frachelstarlive&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=37a3f686\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/user/rachelstarlive</a><br />\n、Facebook頁面<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rachelstarlive\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frachelstarlive&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=7e1ddb7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rachelstarlive</a><br />\n、Instgram帳號<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/rachelstarlive/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Frachelstarlive%2F&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=f7e4359d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/rachelstarlive/</a><br />\n等，其中確實有罹病及痊癒過程之相關照片及敘述文字。<br />\n<br />\nRachel Star Withers曾在她個人 Youtube 頻道影片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZBrgE-hPPxw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZBrgE-hPPxw&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=72bc4352\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZBrgE-hPPxw</a><br />\n中說明臉部肌膚從感染到治癒的過程。<br />\n<br />\n因此，報導中之圖片等媒材是真實而非偽造。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">爭議點二：Rachel Star Withers 是否因為使用公廁洗手乳洗手而導致「全身現血瘡、臉腐蝕如殭屍」？</span><br />\n<br />\n（一）Rachel Star Withers 在她個人 Facebook 頁面上轉貼「公用洗手乳導致臉部潰爛」的報導並加註：<span style=\"color: gold;\">「那些提到給皂器的部分完全是捏造的。」</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fE6uLyY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfE6uLyY.jpg&h=678d45e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（二）查核中心向 Rachel Star Withers 本人求證。她表示：<br />\n<br />\n「...我不知道給皂器這整件事是怎麼來的。 我想最初寫的人是說給皂器、廁所等地方會感染那種細菌。<br />\n<br />\n我說過很多次，醫生們從來沒有確認我感染的究竟是什麼類型的細菌。 其中一個可能是我在旅行中感染－－最有可能是在機場。<br />\n<br />\n我很遺憾這些錯誤訊息四處流傳。 我的照片是公開的，而且看起來很恐怖，這讓人們開始捏造故事。」<br />\n<br />\n（原文：<br />\n<br />\n<em>I have no idea where the whole soap dispenser thing came from. I think originally it was written that one could get that type of bacteria from a soap dispenser, toilet, etc.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">I stated numerous times that the doctors never found out exactly what type of bacteria I had. One of the thoughts was that I picked it up traveling - MOST LIKELY IN AN AIRPORT.<br />\n</span><br />\nI am sorry all of this misinformation has gotten around. My pictures are public and do look scary and people just started making up stuff</em>.）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EGYQu0P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEGYQu0P.jpg&h=23cfa506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRachel Star Withels回信給查核中心的內容（經當事人同意發布）<br />\n<br />\n結論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一、Rachel Star Withers 真有其人，曾受到細菌感染導致臉部肌膚形成病灶，但經過治療已經痊癒。<br />\n<br />\n二、Rachel Star Withers 本人表示：「那些提到給皂器的部分完全是捏造的」。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n因此，「她用公廁洗手乳洗手 竟全身現血瘡、臉腐蝕如殭屍」為【錯誤】訊息。"},{"pid":"732227d06d6f11f525c4253ee2a83fe3e9c4ffd9","tid":1062312,"uid":136763,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:38:09.000Z","msg":"我本身都諗<br />\n有乜可能會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟才疏學淺 <br />\n但件事就好似消毒火酒係溫床 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0023104b32889e12d1d9ee1be04248deb7b46bf5","tid":1062312,"uid":38997,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:39:24.000Z","msg":"CCTVB"},{"pid":"7ee907f4faabb06f61cb7a961aa4a1065bea0947","tid":1062312,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:42:14.000Z","msg":"fake news <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ce3ee0a9cfebe7a34a9b24c1a91fdd25f93dd6","tid":1062312,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:42:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d532638134df45a32b52a53232b4f50d669ccccc","tid":1062312,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T04:48:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0ff330e796a437ffe5093f7874ddf0fa9c321a73","tid":1062312,"uid":7854,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:06:39.000Z","msg":"呢個網正喎"},{"pid":"b28b50327019af3eb05789ebbf87720607918c3e","tid":1062312,"uid":53026,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"龜頭惦到厠板呢？"},{"pid":"564f298ee1ee192575e8f41b0fd1c815d1d6f4b6","tid":1062312,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:24:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"27c1bd3995571759cb27065a829b966734a01fdf","tid":1062312,"uid":402,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"一星期7日洗腦節目"},{"pid":"d348ada194aa0609070d15938b9cd45b4b234fef","tid":1062312,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:14:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2d54ddd203b716a9a071d0c9174febc2bf75cf27","tid":1062312,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:16:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5