":"<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6723609/Simply-washing-hands-public-soap-dispenser-leave-deadly-flesh-eating-bacteria.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-6723609%2FSimply-washing-hands-public-soap-dispenser-leave-deadly-flesh-eating-bacteria.html&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=2bea74bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6723609/Simply-washing-hands-public-soap-dispenser-leave-deadly-flesh-eating-bacteria.html</a><br />\n<br />\n源頭？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T06:56:57.000Z","msg":"萬惡之源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d8c1ccb8b646b5f8d7fcf8073734ed1a5242cc5","tid":1062312,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T07:08:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"57c0e9494b9b02ffeb11dff2de490b8b542b3a31","tid":1062312,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T07:18:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"314bafb30e520065761a02a9feacbb9f4a45e334","tid":1062312,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T07:33:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3c866d40b3898efc9f7f1a96dd4843ac466e21e2","tid":1062312,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T07:35:11.000Z","msg":"搞到我唔敢用"},{"pid":"3deeed223bd66b78a1a95a22ee4b3818df9ba747","tid":1062312,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:47:19.000Z","msg":"push"}]}